## Troubleshooting Protocols

### Common Workup Issues
| Issue | Possible Cause | Diagnostic | Solution |
|-------|----------------|------------|----------|
| Poor phase separation | Emulsion formation | Visual observation | Brine wash, pH adjustment |
| Low extraction yield | Incomplete pH adjustment | pH measurement | Verify pH, repeat extraction |
| Product loss in aqueous | Over-extraction | Mass balance | Reduce extraction cycles |
| Solvent emulsion | High stirring rate | Visual | Reduce agitation |

### Common Crystallization Issues
| Issue | Possible Cause | Diagnostic | Solution |
|-------|----------------|------------|----------|
| No precipitation | Insufficient HCl gas | pH test | Continue gassing |
| Oil formation | Rapid cooling | Visual | Slow cooling, seeding |
| Small crystals | Rapid nucleation | Visual | Controlled cooling |
| Low yield | Solubility issues | Solubility test | Optimize solvent system |

### Common Purification Issues
| Issue | Possible Cause | Diagnostic | Solution |
|-------|----------------|------------|----------|
| Impurities persist | Inadequate recrystallization | TLC analysis | Multiple recrystallizations |
| Low recovery | Excessive washing | Mass balance | Optimize wash volume |
| Crystal form issues | Solvent selection | Microscopy | Alternative solvent system |

